Ayo kita lakukan lagi.

1155
01:31:27,215 --> 01:31:28,883
Kita harus tunggu.

1156
01:31:31,886 --> 01:31:33,179
Dia ke atas.

1157
01:31:34,597 --> 01:31:36,140
Ayo.

